HN10[]  Enforcement, Injunctions
As enacted, the Federal Water Pollution Control Act, 33 U.S.C.S. § 1311(b), calls for the achievement of the best practicable control technology currently available by July 1, 1977, and the best available technology economically achievable by July 1, 1983.

